<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>LSMD Abteilungszentrale Login</title>

    <style>
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            margin: 0;
            min-height: 100vh;
            font-family: Inter, Arial, sans-serif;
            color: #fff;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            background:
                radial-gradient(circle at 12% 18%, rgba(239, 35, 60, 0.28), transparent 30%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 88% 12%, rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.35), transparent 34%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 50% 95%, rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.14), transparent 30%),
                linear-gradient(135deg, #020617 0%, #070b1d 48%, #020617 100%);
        }

        body::before {
            content: "";
            position: fixed;
            inset: 0;
            background-image:
                linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.035) 1px, transparent 1px),
                linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.035) 1px, transparent 1px);
            background-size: 44px 44px;
            animation: gridMove 18s linear infinite;
            pointer-events: none;
            opacity: 0.75;
        }

        .orb {
            position: fixed;
            border-radius: 999px;
            filter: blur(70px);
            opacity: 0.55;
            pointer-events: none;
            animation: orbFloat 8s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        .orb.red {
            width: 420px;
            height: 420px;
            left: -120px;
            bottom: -140px;
            background: rgba(239, 35, 60, 0.38);
        }

        .orb.blue {
            width: 520px;
            height: 520px;
            right: -160px;
            top: -150px;
            background: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.38);
            animation-delay: -3s;
        }

        .page {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: grid;
            place-items: center;
            padding: 46px;
        }

        .command-shell {
            width: min(1320px, 100%);
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 0.9fr 1.1fr;
            gap: 24px;
            align-items: stretch;
        }

        .panel {
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            border-radius: 34px;
            background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.76);
            border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.18);
            box-shadow:
                0 30px 90px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.56),
                inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
            backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
        }

        .panel::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            inset: -2px;
            background:
                linear-gradient(120deg, transparent, rgba(59,130,246,0.30), transparent),
                linear-gradient(300deg, transparent, rgba(239,68,68,0.18), transparent);
            opacity: 0.45;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .login-panel {
            padding: 42px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: space-between;
            min-height: 680px;
        }

        .brand-icon {
            width: 86px;
            height: 86px;
            border-radius: 28px;
            display: grid;
            place-items: center;
            font-size: 38px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ef233c, #991b1b);
            box-shadow: 0 22px 60px rgba(239, 35, 60, 0.45);
            animation: pulse 3s ease-in-out infinite;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        .kicker {
            display: inline-flex;
            width: fit-content;
            padding: 9px 16px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.12);
            border: 1px solid rgba(248, 113, 113, 0.32);
            color: #fecaca;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 950;
            letter-spacing: 0.16em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        h1 {
            margin: 20px 0 16px;
            font-size: clamp(48px, 6vw, 82px);
            line-height: 0.88;
            letter-spacing: -0.075em;
            font-weight: 1000;
        }

        .login-panel p,
        .hero-panel p {
            color: rgba(226, 232, 240, 0.78);
            line-height: 1.65;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .login-btn {
            margin-top: 30px;
            height: 66px;
            border-radius: 22px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 12px;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 950;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1, #2563eb, #06b6d4);
            box-shadow: 0 22px 55px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.42);
            transition: 0.22s ease;
        }

        .login-btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-4px) scale(1.01);
            box-shadow: 0 30px 70px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.58);
            filter: brightness(1.08);
        }

        .access-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 14px;
            margin-top: 28px;
        }

        .access-card,
        .feature-card,
        .status-card {
            border-radius: 22px;
            padding: 18px;
            background: rgba(2, 6, 23, 0.48);
            border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.14);
            transition: 0.22s ease;
        }

        .access-card:hover,
        .feature-card:hover,
        .status-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-4px);
            border-color: rgba(96, 165, 250, 0.40);
            background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.78);
        }

        .access-card h3,
        .feature-card h3,
        .status-card h3 {
            margin: 0 0 6px;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 950;
        }

        .access-card span,
        .feature-card p,
        .status-card span {
            color: rgba(226, 232, 240, 0.72);
            font-size: 13px;
            line-height: 1.45;
        }

        .small-note {
            margin-top: 22px;
            text-align: center;
            color: rgba(226, 232, 240, 0.55);
            font-size: 12px;
        }

        .hero-panel {
            padding: 44px;
            min-height: 680px;
        }

        .online {
            position: absolute;
            right: 44px;
            top: 42px;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            color: #86efac;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 900;
        }

        .online::before {
            content: "";
            width: 10px;
            height: 10px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            background: #22c55e;
            box-shadow: 0 0 18px #22c55e;
        }

        .hero-title {
            margin-top: 28px;
            max-width: 680px;
        }

        .feature-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 14px;
            margin-top: 32px;
        }

        .feature-card {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 14px;
            min-height: 112px;
        }

        .feature-icon {
            width: 48px;
            height: 48px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            display: grid;
            place-items: center;
            background: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.18);
            border: 1px solid rgba(96, 165, 250, 0.25);
            font-size: 22px;
            flex: 0 0 48px;
        }

        .status-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 14px;
            margin-top: 28px;
        }

        .status-card strong {
            color: #86efac;
            font-size: 13px;
        }

        .scanline {
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 1px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(96,165,250,0.75), transparent);
            top: 0;
            animation: scan 5s linear infinite;
            opacity: 0.65;
        }

        @keyframes scan {
            from { top: 0; }
            to { top: 100%; }
        }

        @keyframes pulse {
            0%, 100% { box-shadow: 0 22px 60px rgba(239, 35, 60, 0.45); }
            50% { box-shadow: 0 30px 85px rgba(239, 35, 60, 0.68); }
        }

        @keyframes gridMove {
            from { background-position: 0 0; }
            to { background-position: 44px 44px; }
        }

        @keyframes orbFloat {
            0%, 100% { transform: translate(0,0); }
            50% { transform: translate(35px,-30px); }
        }

        @media (max-width: 1050px) {
            .command-shell {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            .login-panel,
            .hero-panel {
                min-height: auto;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 650px) {
            .page {
                padding: 16px;
            }

            .login-panel,
            .hero-panel {
                padding: 26px;
                border-radius: 26px;
            }

            .access-grid,
            .feature-grid,
            .status-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            h1 {
                font-size: 48px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="orb red"></div>
    <div class="orb blue"></div>

    <main class="page">
        <section class="command-shell">
            <div class="panel login-panel">
                <div class="scanline"></div>

                <div>
                    <div class="brand-icon">🚑</div>
                    <div class="kicker">LSMD Access System</div>

                    <h1>LSMD<br>Abteilungs<br>Zentrale</h1>

                    <p>
                        Melde dich mit Discord an und verwalte Ausbildung, Overwatch,
                        Punkte, Dokumente und interne Abteilungssysteme zentral an einem Ort.
                    </p>

                    <% if (typeof error !== "undefined" && error) { %>
                        <p style="color:#fecaca;font-weight:900;"><%= error %></p>
                    <% } %>

                    <a href="/auth/discord" class="login-btn">
                        <span>💬</span>
                        Mit Discord einloggen
                    </a>

                    <div class="access-grid">
                        <div class="access-card">
                            <h3>Admin</h3>
                            <span>Voller Zugriff</span>
                        </div>

                        <div class="access-card">
                            <h3>Abteilungen</h3>
                            <span>Rollenbasierter Zugriff</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="small-note">
                    Zugriff nur mit gültiger Discord-Rolle.
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="panel hero-panel">
                <div class="scanline"></div>
                <div class="online">Online</div>

                <div class="kicker">Live System</div>

                <h1 class="hero-title">Abteilungen.<br>Systeme.<br>Kontrolle.</h1>

                <p>
                    Die LSMD Abteilungszentrale verbindet Discord-Login, Rollenprüfung,
                    Punkteverwaltung, Lizenzsysteme, Dokumente und interne Verwaltung
                    in einem modernen System.
                </p>

                <div class="feature-grid">
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <div class="feature-icon">🏥</div>
                        <div>
                            <h3>Abteilungen</h3>
                            <p>Prakti/Sani, Overwatch und interne LSMD-Bereiche zentral verwalten.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <div class="feature-icon">👁️</div>
                        <div>
                            <h3>Overwatch-System</h3>
                            <p>Lizenzen, Auffrischungen und Prüfer sauber dokumentieren.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <div class="feature-icon">📄</div>
                        <div>
                            <h3>Dokumente</h3>
                            <p>Leitfäden, Regelwerke und Checklisten zentral abrufen.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <div class="feature-icon">🛡️</div>
                        <div>
                            <h3>Admin Tools</h3>
                            <p>Interne Panels, Rechte und Systeme übersichtlich steuern.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="status-grid">
                    <div class="status-card">
                        <h3>Discord</h3>
                        <strong>Verbunden</strong>
                    </div>

                    <div class="status-card">
                        <h3>MongoDB</h3>
                        <strong>Online</strong>
                    </div>

                    <div class="status-card">
                        <h3>LSMD</h3>
                        <strong>Bereit</strong>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</body>
</html>